@startuml get_user

title GET /users e GET /users/{id} — Buscar Usuário

actor User
boundary "Frontend" as FE
participant "UserController" as Ctrl
participant "GetUserUseCase" as UC
participant "UserMapper" as Mapper
participant "UserRepositoryPort" as Repo
database "users" as DB

== Listar todos ==

User -> FE: solicita listagem de usuários
activate FE
FE -> Ctrl: GET /users
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> UC: findAll()
activate UC

UC -> Repo: findAll()
activate Repo
Repo -> DB: SELECT * FROM users\nWHERE status != DELETED
DB --> Repo: List<User>
Repo --> UC: List<User>
deactivate Repo

UC -> Mapper: toResponse(each user)
activate Mapper
Mapper --> UC: List<UserResponse>
deactivate Mapper

UC --> Ctrl: List<UserResponse>
deactivate UC
Ctrl --> FE: 200 OK {List<UserResponse>}
deactivate Ctrl
FE --> User: exibe listagem
deactivate FE

== Buscar por ID ==

User -> FE: solicita busca por ID
activate FE
FE -> Ctrl: GET /users/{id}
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> UC: findById(id)
activate UC

UC -> Repo: findById(UserId.of(id))
activate Repo
Repo -> DB: SELECT * FROM users\nWHERE id=? AND status!=DELETED
DB --> Repo: Optional<User>
Repo --> UC: Optional<User>
deactivate Repo

alt found
  UC -> Mapper: toResponse(user)
  activate Mapper
  Mapper --> UC: UserResponse
  deactivate Mapper

  UC --> Ctrl: UserResponse
  Ctrl --> FE: 200 OK {UserResponse}
  FE --> User: exibe dados
else not found
  UC --> Ctrl: ResourceNotFoundException
  Ctrl --> FE: 404 Not Found
  FE --> User: exibe erro
end

deactivate UC
deactivate Ctrl
deactivate FE

@enduml
